<paragraph id="8BA83A22EB77FFC4FF24ED39FD62F813" blockId="9.[151,1436,1764,2043]" pageId="9" pageNumber="352">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB77FFC4FF24ED39FE2AF8BF" bold="true" box="[199,454,1800,1827]" pageId="9" pageNumber="352">Original description:</emphasis>
not described. This taxon was never formally described, but only figured in 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB77FFC4FAB3ED39FF02F8DB" author="Bellini, R." pageId="9" pageNumber="352" pagination="85 - 121" refId="ref15636" refString="Bellini, R. (1902 a) Contribuzione alla conoscenza della fauna dei molluschi marini dell'isola di Capri. Bollettino della Societa dei Naturalisti in Napoli, Series 1, 15, 85 - 121." type="journal article" year="1902">Bellini (1902a)</bibRefCitation>
under the name “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB77FFC4FE5DED1CFBA2F8DB" authority="Monterosato" authorityName="Monterosato" box="[446,1102,1836,1863]" class="Gastropoda" family="Cerithiidae" genus="Bittium" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="9" pageNumber="352" phylum="Mollusca" rank="variety" species="iadertinum" variety="coralligena">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB77FFC4FE5DED1CFD78F8DA" box="[446,660,1836,1862]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="352">Bittium iadertinum</emphasis>
Brusina var. 
<emphasis id="B963E630EB77FFC4FCD3ED1DFC5DF8DA" box="[816,945,1836,1862]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="352">coralligena</emphasis>
Monterosato
</taxonomicName>
”. Monterosato also never described this taxon (see 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB77FFC4FE7AED61FD63F8F7" author="Appolloni, M. &amp; Smriglio, C. &amp; Amati, B. &amp; Luglie, L. &amp; Nofroni, I. &amp; Tringali, L. P. &amp; Mariottini, P. &amp; Oliverio, M." box="[409,655,1872,1899]" pageId="9" pageNumber="352" pagination="1 - 138" refId="ref15382" refString="Appolloni, M., Smriglio, C., Amati, B., Luglie, L., Nofroni, I., Tringali, L. P., Mariottini, P. &amp; Oliverio, M. (2018) Catalogue of the primary types of marine molluscan taxa described by Tommaso Allery Di Maria, Marquis of Monterosato, deposited in the Museo Civico di Zoologia, Roma. Zootaxa, 4477 (1), 1 - 138. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4477.1.1" type="journal article" year="2018">
Appolloni 
<emphasis id="B963E630EB77FFC4FDF0ED60FDA0F8F6" box="[531,588,1872,1898]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="352">et al.</emphasis>
2018
</bibRefCitation>
), and thus this name is available due to 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB77FFC4FBB0ED61FB1AF8F7" author="Bellini, R." box="[1107,1270,1872,1899]" pageId="9" pageNumber="352" pagination="85 - 121" refId="ref15636" refString="Bellini, R. (1902 a) Contribuzione alla conoscenza della fauna dei molluschi marini dell'isola di Capri. Bollettino della Societa dei Naturalisti in Napoli, Series 1, 15, 85 - 121." type="journal article" year="1902">Bellini (1902)</bibRefCitation>
’s figures, published before 1931 (
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB77FFC4FE95ED44FE10F813" author="ICZN &amp; International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature" box="[374,508,1909,1935]" pageId="9" pageNumber="352" refId="ref17437" refString="ICZN [International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature] (2012) International code of zoological nomenclature. 4 th Edition. International Trust for Zoological Nomenclature, London. Available from: http: // www. iczn. org / (accessed 15 Feburary 2019)" type="url" year="2012">ICZN 2012</bibRefCitation>
: Art. 11, 12).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BA83A22EB77FFC4FF24EDA9FC9DF867" blockId="9.[151,1436,1764,2043]" pageId="9" pageNumber="352">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB77FFC4FF24EDA9FE5FF82F" bold="true" box="[199,435,1944,1971]" pageId="9" pageNumber="352">Material examined:</emphasis>
15 shells labelled by Bellini “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB77FFC4FCE4EDA8FA7FF82E" authority="Mtros-Capri" authorityName="Mtros-Capri" box="[775,1427,1944,1971]" class="Gastropoda" family="Cerithiidae" genus="Bittium" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="9" pageNumber="352" phylum="Mollusca" rank="variety" species="iadertinum" variety="coralligenum">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB77FFC4FCE4EDA8FC30F82E" box="[775,988,1944,1970]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="352">Bittium iadertinum</emphasis>
Brus. 
<emphasis id="B963E630EB77FFC4FBC5EDA8FB07F82E" box="[1062,1259,1944,1970]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="352">var. coralligenum</emphasis>
Mtros—Capri
</taxonomicName>
” (MCZR—not numbered) actually belong to 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB77FFC4FD72ED8CFBFEF84B" authority="Brusina, 1865" authorityName="Brusina" authorityYear="1865" box="[657,1042,1980,2007]" class="Gastropoda" family="Cerithiidae" genus="Bittium" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="9" pageNumber="352" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="jadertinum">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB77FFC4FD72ED8CFC8BF84A" box="[657,871,1980,2006]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="352">Bittium jadertinum</emphasis>
Brusina, 1865
</taxonomicName>
, now a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB77FFC4FAA9ED8CFD30F867" authority="(da Costa, 1778) (MolluscaBase 2019 c)" authorityName="da Costa" authorityYear="1778" baseAuthorityName="da Costa" baseAuthorityYear="1778" class="Gastropoda" family="Cerithiidae" genus="Bittium" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="9" pageNumber="352" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="reticulatum">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB77FFC4FAA9ED8CFEFBF866" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="352">Bittium reticulatum</emphasis>
(da Costa, 1778) (MolluscaBase 2019c)
</taxonomicName>
(
<figureCitation id="132C26A7EB77FFC4FD08EDD1FC88F867" box="[747,868,2016,2043]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="12.[151,250,1460,1485]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,395,1432]" captionTargetId="figure@12.[151,1436,414,1432]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="FIGURE 4. A–C. Bittium iadertinum var. coralligena. A. Original figures. B. Possible type material from Capri Island (Naples)—4.9×1.5 mm. C. Original label handwritten by Bellini. MCZR—not numbered. D, E. Murex trunculus var. propeconglobata. D. Fossil(?) shell from Sciacca (Agrigento)—72.4×52.8 mm. E. Original label handwritten by Monterosato. MCZR- M-7623. F, G. Fusus (Pseudofusus) pulchellus var. curta. F. Original figures. G. Shells from Capri Island (Naples) and original label handwritten by Monterosato (up to 16 mm in total height). MCCIC—drawer 8, n. 146. H. Clathromangilia granum var. prausi. Original figures. I. Left. Cardium (Parvicardium) exiguum var. minimum. Original figure. I. Right. Cardium (Parvicardium) exiguum var. paludosum. Original figures." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3449572" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3449572/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="352">Fig. 4B, C</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C30D69A9EB74FFC7FF24EAA8FE15FD87" pageId="10" pageNumber="353" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BA83A22EB74FFC7FF24EAA8FE15FD87" blockId="10.[151,1437,152,539]" pageId="10" pageNumber="353">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB74FFC7FF24EAA8FED1FF2F" bold="true" box="[199,317,153,179]" pageId="10" pageNumber="353">Remarks:</emphasis>
having been instituted as a 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB74FFC7FD8EEAA8FCFFFF2E" box="[621,787,152,179]" pageId="10" pageNumber="353" rank="subSpecies" subSpecies="connected">race connected</taxonomicName>
to a specific habitat, we rank it subspecific, and thus available (
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB74FFC7FF36EA8CFEB0FF4B" author="ICZN &amp; International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature" box="[213,348,189,215]" pageId="10" pageNumber="353" refId="ref17437" refString="ICZN [International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature] (2012) International code of zoological nomenclature. 4 th Edition. International Trust for Zoological Nomenclature, London. Available from: http: // www. iczn. org / (accessed 15 Feburary 2019)" type="url" year="2012">ICZN 2012</bibRefCitation>
: Art. 10, glossary). Strangely, 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB74FFC7FD57EA8CFC30FF4B" author="Praus Franceschini, C." box="[692,988,188,215]" pageId="10" pageNumber="353" pagination="1 - 68" refId="ref18743" refString="Praus Franceschini, C. (1906) Elenco delle conchiglie del Golfo di Napoli e del Mediterraneo esistenti nel Museo Zoologico di Napoli. Annuario del Museo Zoologico della R. Universita di Napoli, 2 (5), 1 - 68." type="journal article" year="1906">Praus Franceschini (1906)</bibRefCitation>
listed “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB74FFC7FBD0EA8CFB0BFF4A" box="[1075,1255,188,215]" class="Gastropoda" family="Cerithiidae" genus="Bittium" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="10" pageNumber="353" phylum="Mollusca" rank="variety" species="iadertinum" variety="coralligena">
var. 
<emphasis id="B963E630EB74FFC7FB85EA8DFB0BFF4A" box="[1126,1255,188,214]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="353">coralligena</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
” as a variety of 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB74FFC7FF74EAD0FDDFFF67" authority="(Payraudeau, 1826)" authorityName="Payraudeau" authorityYear="1826" baseAuthorityName="Payraudeau" baseAuthorityYear="1826" box="[151,563,224,251]" class="Gastropoda" family="Cerithiidae" genus="Bittium" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="10" pageNumber="353" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="latreillei">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB74FFC7FF74EAD0FEBCFF66" box="[151,336,224,250]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="353">Bittium latreillei</emphasis>
(Payraudeau, 1826)
</taxonomicName>
and “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB74FFC7FD90EAD0FC8AFF67" authority="Mtrs." authorityName="Mtrs." box="[627,870,224,251]" class="Gastropoda" family="Cerithiidae" genus="Bittium" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="10" pageNumber="353" phylum="Mollusca" rank="variety" species="iadertinum" variety="corallinum">
var. 
<emphasis id="B963E630EB74FFC7FD45EAD1FCCDFF66" box="[678,801,224,250]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="353">corallinum</emphasis>
Mtrs.
</taxonomicName>
” as a variety of 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB74FFC7FBFEEAD0FA74FF67" authority="Brusina, 1865" authorityName="Brusina" authorityYear="1865" box="[1053,1432,224,251]" class="Gastropoda" family="Cerithiidae" genus="Bittium" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="10" pageNumber="353" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="jadertinum">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB74FFC7FBFEEAD0FB1DFF66" box="[1053,1265,224,250]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="353">Bittium jadertinum</emphasis>
Brusina, 1865
</taxonomicName>
, thus raising doubts as to whether or not he cited the taxon introduced by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB74FFC7FC5FEB35FB85FE83" author="Bellini, R." box="[956,1129,260,287]" pageId="10" pageNumber="353" pagination="85 - 121" refId="ref15636" refString="Bellini, R. (1902 a) Contribuzione alla conoscenza della fauna dei molluschi marini dell'isola di Capri. Bollettino della Societa dei Naturalisti in Napoli, Series 1, 15, 85 - 121." type="journal article" year="1902">Bellini (1902a)</bibRefCitation>
. Material belonging to both taxa was deposited in the MZF2 museum by himself, thus not constituting the original 
<typeStatus id="54AC8480EB74FFC7FB60EB18FB2EFEDF" box="[1155,1218,297,323]" pageId="10" pageNumber="353">types</typeStatus>
; such material was also not found by us in MZF2. Also 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB74FFC7FDD8EB7DFD0AFEFB" author="Bellini, R." box="[571,742,332,359]" pageId="10" pageNumber="353" pagination="1 - 87" refId="ref15827" refString="Bellini, R. (1929 a) I molluschi del Golfo di Napoli (studi precedenti, l'ambiente, enumerazione e sinonimia). Annuario del Museo Zoologico della R. Universita di Napoli, 6 (2), 1 - 87." type="journal article" year="1929">Bellini (1929a)</bibRefCitation>
only listed 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB74FFC7FC8CEB7CFB16FEFA" box="[879,1274,332,359]" class="Gastropoda" family="Cerithiidae" genus="Bittium" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="10" pageNumber="353" phylum="Mollusca" rank="variety" species="iadertinum" variety="corallinum">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB74FFC7FC8CEB7CFBA9FEFA" box="[879,1093,332,358]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="353">Bittium iadertinum</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B963E630EB74FFC7FB9CEB7DFB16FEFA" box="[1151,1274,332,358]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="353">corallinum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in his general overview of the marine molluscan species living in the Gulf of Naples, thus apparently skipping his own taxon. No other mention to 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB74FFC7FE62EBA4FC5FFE33" authority="Bellini, 1902 a" authorityName="Bellini" authorityYear="1902" box="[385,947,404,431]" class="Gastropoda" family="Cerithiidae" genus="Bittium" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="10" pageNumber="353" phylum="Mollusca" rank="variety" species="iadertinum" variety="coralligena">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB74FFC7FE62EBA4FDB9FE32" box="[385,597,404,430]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="353">Bittium iadertinum</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B963E630EB74FFC7FD6EEBA5FCE2FE32" box="[653,782,404,430]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="353">coralligena</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB74FFC7FCF6EBA5FC5FFE33" author="Bellini, R." box="[789,947,404,431]" pageId="10" pageNumber="353" pagination="85 - 121" refId="ref15636" refString="Bellini, R. (1902 a) Contribuzione alla conoscenza della fauna dei molluschi marini dell'isola di Capri. Bollettino della Societa dei Naturalisti in Napoli, Series 1, 15, 85 - 121." type="journal article" year="1902">Bellini, 1902a</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
was found in the subsequent malacological literature. Taking into account the complex taxonomy of the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C1741A1EB74FFC7FC70EB88FB82FE4F" authority="Gray, 1847" authorityName="Gray" authorityYear="1847" box="[915,1134,441,467]" class="Gastropoda" family="Cerithiidae" genus="Bittium" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="10" pageNumber="353" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B963E630EB74FFC7FC70EB88FC09FE4E" box="[915,997,441,466]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="353">Bittium</emphasis>
Gray, 1847
</taxonomicName>
, as well as the low quality of the original figures, this taxon may fit several congeneric Mediterranean taxa, and thus it is considered a 
<emphasis id="B963E630EB74FFC7FAB1EBECFF07FD86" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="353">nomen dubium</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EF8647D3EB74FFC7FF19E830FE6CFD87" author="ICZN &amp; International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature" box="[250,384,513,539]" pageId="10" pageNumber="353" refId="ref17437" refString="ICZN [International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature] (2012) International code of zoological nomenclature. 4 th Edition. International Trust for Zoological Nomenclature, London. Available from: http: // www. iczn. org / (accessed 15 Feburary 2019)" type="url" year="2012">ICZN 2012</bibRefCitation>
: glossary).
</paragraph>
